  its needed to read Mpeg-TS files. Bug #405267

  20 Feb 2012; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> vlc-2.0.0.ebuild:
  drop arm keyword prior to unmasking for bug #397891

  20 Feb 2012; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> vlc-2.0.0.ebuild,
